  "2187160": {
    "name": "东方迷你乡",
    "steam_appid": 2187160,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃离现实的喧嚣，踏入宁静治愈的东方幻境 ——《东方迷你乡》以策略与益智交织的独特玩法，邀你用指尖拼凑专属的村落盛景，在慢节奏的探索中感受东方世界的温柔魅力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187160/extras/09ce5c806bc152659ae1ac2a0fe5b063.avif?t=1769582552\" width=616 height=98 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款兼顾休闲解压与策略挑战的益智佳作：游戏开局，你将获得一叠程序化生成的地景板块，从最上层抽取后，选择未开发区域放置，通过旋转调整最佳角度，组合出森林、小镇、河流等不同规模的村落地形，以此获取高分。每一局的板块组合都不重复，让探索之路始终充满新鲜感，耐玩性十足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187160/extras/dae1ee7b1abce7cc62589dd4d5687ee8.poster.avif?t=1769582552\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187160/extras/dae1ee7b1abce7cc62589dd4d5687ee8.webm?t=1769582552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187160/extras/dae1ee7b1abce7cc62589dd4d5687ee8.mp4?t=1769582552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集爱心可解锁更多地景板块，积累积分则能开启全新地图区域 —— 每个关卡都藏有独特的生态板块与专属东方人物，随着版图扩张，你不仅能发掘多样生物群系，还会遇到附带奖励的特殊地景板块，完成挑战即可解锁更多板块类型、拓展任务线，让建造之旅愈发丰富。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是想抽离繁忙日常，沉浸在乡间田野的静谧风光中放松身心；还是想发挥策略思维，通过精妙布局冲击 Steam 排行榜高分，都能在这款游戏中找到归属。原创桌游风格的美术设计，将东方世界的奇幻与田园的清新完美融合，每一处场景都宛如可触摸的实体桌游画面，治愈感拉满。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187160/extras/a93100d573f39e60d9c1fe996518aa7a.poster.avif?t=1769582552\" width=616 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187160/extras/a93100d573f39e60d9c1fe996518aa7a.webm?t=1769582552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187160/extras/a93100d573f39e60d9c1fe996518aa7a.mp4?t=1769582552\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187160/extras/6b393b0ca276f3817fb778bdcdfd65be.avif?t=1769582552\" width=616 height=98 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >双重游玩体验：既适合休闲玩家放松身心，也能满足策略爱好者挑战高分</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特玩法机制：地景板块组合 + 积分解锁，程序化生成确保每局不重复</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富收集元素：多样生态板块、东方人物、生物群系待你解锁</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >治愈系美术风格：原创桌游质感画面，还原东方世界的清新与奇幻</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >低门槛高耐玩：操作简单易上手，策略深度拉满，碎片化时间也能畅玩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam 专属支持：27 项成就、排行榜比拼、云存档同步与家庭共享功能</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支持与配置</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >语言适配：简体中文、英语（界面与字幕全覆盖）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >低配置友好：仅需 350MB 存储空间，入门电脑即可流畅运行</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187160/extras/ada5589bffba17bb5cf3abdc878741ce.avif?t=1769582552\" width=616 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >值得一提的是，《东方迷你乡》源自一位初入东方世界的开发者对这个 IP 的爱与向往 —— 东方的魅力值得慢慢发掘，而我们也希望你能在这款充满诚意的作品中，收获属于自己的宁静与乐趣。</p>",
